  "body": "Noticed a very strange behavior when rendering the same chart (parent chart with sub charts) shows different results. Basically I just do Arrow UP and Enter and  without any modifications this renders differently:\r\n! Working case\r\nkind: PersistentVolumeClaim\r\nmetadata:\r\n  name: glance-test\r\n! Incorrectly working case\r\nkind: PersistentVolumeClaim\r\nmetadata:\r\n  name:   \r\n\r\nI managed to collect strace for working and non working case and I see in non-working case common macro file located in parent chart's template folder does not get opened, when in the working case you can clearly see it gets opened.\r\n\r\nAttaching the complete strace log for both cases for review.\r\n[changing values log dec 16 2016.txt](https://github.com/kubernetes/helm/files/657154/changing.values.log.dec.16.2016.txt)\r\n",
